title: Severin Freund takes German national title (FIS - Fédération Internationale de Ski)
text: ( Source : FIS - Fédération Internationale de Ski ) Severin Freund dominated the German national championships on the large hill in Garmisch-Partenkirchen. Last winter's overall World Cup winner showed the best jumps in both rounds with 138.5
